dataSource.query:
SELECT
	 event_name AS Variant,
    "Number of Cases",
    "Time until delivery picked (days)",
    "Time until GI posted (days)",
    "Delivery items with actual picking request after planned picking date (%)",
    "Delivery items with goods issue posting later than planned (%)"
FROM (
	SELECT
    	count(case_id) AS "Number of Cases",
        event_name AS Variant,
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Delivery items picked") 
        	AS "Time until delivery picked (days)",
		AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Delivery items with goods issue posted") 
        	AS "Time until GI posted (days)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Delivery items with actual picking request after planned picking date") * 100 
        	AS "Delivery items with actual picking request after planned picking date (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Delivery items with goods issue posting later than planned") * 100 
        	AS "Delivery items with goods issue posting later than planned (%)"
	FROM THIS_PROCESS
	GROUP BY 2
) AS sub
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5
